member.name: CERT_DH_PARAMETERS
member.summary: The CERT_DH_PARAMETERS structure contains parameters associated with a Diffie/Hellman public key algorithm.

member.name: CERT_DH_PARAMETERS.p
member.summary: Prime modulus P. The most significant bit of the most significant byte must always be set to 1.

member.name: CERT_DH_PARAMETERS.g
member.summary: Generator G. Must be the same length as p (must be padded with 0x00 bytes if it is less).
